   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Tothoes the agent for the quarter (tax) from the millers of Oxyrhyncha and the adjacent villages for the 4th year to Oaphres, greeting. I have received from you the contribution for Mecheir of the 4th year. Good-bye. The 4th year, Mecheir 17. (on the verso; 2nd h.) I, Maron, have written.</ab>
